WEBVTT

00:06.000 --> 00:12.074
Advertise your product or brand here
contact www.OpenSubtitles.org today

00:14.520 --> 00:17.440
How many more times?
Two more should square it.

00:17.441 --> 00:19.080
One.

00:22.400 --> 00:24.358
Do you know what they did
in the Old Testament

00:24.359 --> 00:26.920
to people who reneged
on their debts?

00:28.480 --> 00:31.400
Stoned them to death.
Caved their heads in.

00:31.401 --> 00:33.200
That's not true.

00:35.000 --> 00:36.999
Take a look. I don't need to.

00:37.000 --> 00:38.719
Unlike you, I've read it.

00:38.720 --> 00:41.479
I bet. Cover to cover.

00:41.480 --> 00:42.880
Good little Catholic girl.

00:47.280 --> 00:49.440
You're just being a good wife,
remember?

00:51.720 --> 00:53.360
Let me hear you say it.

00:55.760 --> 00:57.000
I'm a good wife.

00:58.680 --> 01:00.360
If you ever doubt that...

01:02.680 --> 01:07.279
then remember,
if I don't get what I'm owed,

01:07.280 --> 01:11.720
I'll turn you from a wife
to a widow in the blink of an eye.

01:15.160 --> 01:16.440
I swear it.

01:20.120 --> 01:21.680
So help me, God.

01:31.230 --> 01:52.191
